{"tid":182001,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過講去日本旅行比人笑？","createTime":"2017-04-01T04:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T02:07:03.000Z","uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"799b75f04a54de91460a83f7cfa952851dd9be7c","tid":182001,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"好好地去個旅行，計劃好晒行程，睇靚景食好野，<br />\n轉個頭就比人話無眼光、購物團，要去就去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連屋企人都唔太鐘意我去，成日叫我返大陸望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3620c9d4f44a56f71acc6534589766109764807c","tid":182001,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55dfbce779097ef7289cfb62e07169f7d99a8bd4","tid":182001,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真去四次日本都已經見怪不怪，<br />\n只係每次聽到都有少少心煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a7fb7c0529178cf7642b448d00380af9657dd0","tid":182001,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真去四次日本都已經見怪不怪，<br />\n只係每次聽到都有少少心煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人一年都唔止四次<br />\n仲要完全唔識日文"},{"pid":"5415f7414afb54d8f5e69055a6207364bb82c30c","tid":182001,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"佢地有無去過日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6c6383e92c0cba12cefda71c31255af0257030","tid":182001,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真去四次日本都已經見怪不怪，<br />\n只係每次聽到都有少少心煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人一年都唔止四次<br />\n仲要完全唔識日文</blockquote><br />\n又無可能自私到叫個班人唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係你見佢地係日本周街問人「Hong Kong people?」咁求救，<br />\n真心唔識比反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖則話去日本係平過去歐洲，但旅行呢家野唔係要鬥貴嫁嘛&hellip;"},{"pid":"6a1b4dc30b482116970c8a11d73d46c8594011d0","tid":182001,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"唔會，識聽日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD囡對眼發哂光"},{"pid":"01c9b056e2fa9fb5b739c59f52a1f80cc91b0d27","tid":182001,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真去四次日本都已經見怪不怪，<br />\n只係每次聽到都有少少心煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人一年都唔止四次<br />\n仲要完全唔識日文</blockquote><br />\n又無可能自私到叫個班人唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係你見佢地係日本周街問人「Hong Kong people?」咁求救，<br />\n真心唔識比反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖則話去日本係平過去歐洲，但旅行呢家野唔係要鬥貴嫁嘛&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n去半年歐洲一直都好掛住日本好想去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩種完全唔同感覺唔同玩法，兩種都鐘意"},{"pid":"27607a7e848f0b3e8f8574b27fd0f5393306263b","tid":182001,"uid":60156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:31:16.000Z","msg":"試過有次係東京箱根落雪無帶外套，得負2度..用左條毛巾當頸巾用比2個日本妹子笑完仲要影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1eafe38276679e2451440874d2124ce04bc2d94","tid":182001,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過有次係東京箱根落雪無帶外套，得負2度..用左條毛巾當頸巾用比2個日本妹子笑完仲要影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8bf1d3305c071b9be116f333107d56f2cbf6bf","tid":182001,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:59:49.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆, 好多人對日本既認知就係shopping, 完。"},{"pid":"68d6777b39d7166b6140ad7579d57451fd00fa75","tid":182001,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老豆豆, 好多人對日本既認知就係shopping, 完。</blockquote><br />\n同埋叫雞"},{"pid":"0d79fa05383f345a67e542698acdd99ed3e970f7","tid":182001,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老老豆豆, 好多人對日本既認知就係shopping, 完。</blockquote><br />\n同埋叫雞</blockquote><br />\n叫雞？係都返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06a68ca6839dc978fbda08ee1133dd33bc9cce3","tid":182001,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:41:00.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要笑人去旅行嘅目的地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會咁做嘅好